					Full Description



		Kuwait Telecommunications Company KSCP is a Kuwait-based company engaged in the provision of cellular mobile telecommunication and data services in accordance with the principles of Islamic Shari’a. The Company focuses on the purchase, supply, install, operate and maintain wireless telecommunications devices and equipment (mobile telecommunications, calling system and other wireless services). The Company’s offerings are structured into two divisions: Personal, which includes postpaid, prepaid, fourth generation long-term evolution (4G LTE), devices, iPhone, surf on, promotions, rewards and other related services, and Business, which includes voice solutions, Internet services, smart solutions, business solutions. The Company is a subsidiary of Saudi Telecommunications Company.
» Full Overview of VIVA.KW







