Business Summary


Provides telecommunication servicesKuwait Telecommunications Co. engages in the provision of cellular mobile telecommunication and data services.Its activities include the purchase, supply, installation, operation, and maintenance of wireless telecommunication devices and equipment.Kuwait Telecommunications products include personal and business solutions, such as postpaid, prepaid and internet.The company was founded on June 24, 2008 and is headquartered in Kuwait City, Kuwait.

 





